{{#base headerTitle="Weekly Stale Leads Reminder" headerSubtitle="Time to re-engage your prospects!"}}

<div class="greeting">
    Hello {{name}}! üìä
</div>

<div class="info-notice">
    <p>üìÖ <strong>Week of {{weekOf}}:</strong> You have leads that need immediate attention! These prospects are going cold and need your re-engagement to keep them in your pipeline.</p>
</div>

<div class="message">
    <p>Stale leads are opportunities waiting to be rekindled. Studies show that leads contacted within 7 days have a 5x higher conversion rate. Don't let these valuable prospects slip away!</p>
</div>

<div class="info-card">
    <h3>üìà Weekly Summary</h3>
    <div class="detail-grid">
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Total Stale Leads</span>
            <span class="detail-value"><strong>{{totalCount}}</strong></span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Never Contacted</span>
            <span class="detail-value"><strong>{{neverContactedCount}}</strong></span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">High Priority</span>
            <span class="detail-value"><strong>{{highPriorityCount}}</strong></span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Total Potential Value</span>
            <span class="detail-value"><strong>R{{formatNumber totalEstimatedValue}}</strong></span>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

{{#if staleLeads}}
<div class="info-card">
    <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Stale Leads Requiring Immediate Action</h3>
    
    {{#each staleLeads}}
    <div class="lead-item" style="border: 1px solid #e1e5e9; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; background-color: #fafbfc;">
        <div class="lead-header" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 12px;">
            <h4 style="margin: 0; color: #172b4d; font-size: 16px;">{{name}}</h4>
            <span class="urgency-badge" style="padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; background-color: #ffebe6; color: #de350b;">
                {{#eq daysSinceLastContact 'Never contacted'}}NEVER CONTACTED{{else}}{{daysSinceLastContact}} DAYS STALE{{/eq}}
            </span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="lead-details" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px;">
            <div>
                <span style="font-weight: 600; color: #5e6c84;">Company:</span>
                <span style="color: #172b4d;">{{companyName}}</span>
            </div>
            <div>
                <span style="font-weight: 600; color: #5e6c84;">Email:</span>
                <span style="color: #172b4d;">{{email}}</span>
            </div>
            <div>
                <span style="font-weight: 600; color: #5e6c84;">Phone:</span>
                <span style="color: #172b4d;">{{phone}}</span>
            </div>
            <div>
                <span style="font-weight: 600; color: #5e6c84;">Temperature:</span>
                <span class="temp-badge {{temperature}}" style="padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold;
                    {{#eq temperature 'HOT'}}background-color: #ffebe6; color: #de350b;{{/eq}}
                    {{#eq temperature 'WARM'}}background-color: #fff4e6; color: #ff8b00;{{/eq}}
                    {{#eq temperature 'COLD'}}background-color: #e6fcff; color: #0065ff;{{/eq}}
                    {{#eq temperature 'FROZEN'}}background-color: #f4f5f7; color: #6b778c;{{/eq}}">
                    {{temperature}}
                </span>
            </div>
            <div>
                <span style="font-weight: 600; color: #5e6c84;">Priority:</span>
                <span class="priority-badge {{priority}}" style="padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold;
                    {{#eq priority 'HIGH'}}background-color: #ffebe6; color: #de350b;{{/eq}}
                    {{#eq priority 'MEDIUM'}}background-color: #fff4e6; color: #ff8b00;{{/eq}}
                    {{#eq priority 'LOW'}}background-color: #e3fcef; color: #006644;{{/eq}}">
                    {{priority}}
                </span>
            </div>
            <div>
                <span style="font-weight: 600; color: #5e6c84;">Est. Value:</span>
                <span style="color: #006644; font-weight: 600;">R{{formatNumber estimatedValue}}</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="lead-timing" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr)); gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 8px; background-color: #f4f5f7; border-radius: 4px;">
            <div>
                <span style="font-weight: 600; color: #5e6c84; font-size: 12px;">Created:</span>
                <span style="color: #172b4d; font-weight: 600; font-size: 12px;">{{daysSinceCreated}} days ago</span>
            </div>
            <div>
                <span style="font-weight: 600; color: #5e6c84; font-size: 12px;">Last Contact:</span>
                <span style="color: {{#eq daysSinceLastContact 'Never contacted'}}#de350b{{else}}#172b4d{{/eq}}; font-weight: 600; font-size: 12px;">
                    {{lastContactDate}}
                </span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        {{#if notes}}
        <div class="lead-notes" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">
            <span style="font-weight: 600; color: #5e6c84; font-size: 12px;">Notes:</span>
            <p style="margin: 4px 0 0 0; color: #172b4d; font-size: 12px; font-style: italic;">"{{notes}}"</p>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
        
        <div class="lead-actions" style="text-align: right;">
            <a href="{{../dashboardUrl}}/leads/{{uid}}" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #0052cc; color: white; padding: 8px 16px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">
                Contact Now
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
    {{/each}}
</div>

<div class="cta-section">
    <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}/leads" class="cta-button">View All Leads in Dashboard</a>
</div>

<div class="info-card">
    <h4>üî• Re-engagement Strategies for Stale Leads</h4>
    <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><strong>Never Contacted:</strong> Start with a warm, personalized introduction highlighting your value proposition</li>
        <li><strong>Old Leads:</strong> Reference previous conversations and provide new, relevant information</li>
        <li><strong>High Priority:</strong> Make a direct phone call or schedule a meeting immediately</li>
        <li><strong>Cold Leads:</strong> Try a different communication channel (email ‚Üí call ‚Üí social media)</li>
        <li><strong>Company Leads:</strong> Research recent company news or developments to create relevance</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="info-card">
    <h4>üìû Suggested Contact Approach</h4>
    <ol class="feature-list">
        <li><strong>Acknowledge the Gap:</strong> "I realize it's been a while since we connected..."</li>
        <li><strong>Provide Value:</strong> Share relevant industry insights or new solutions</li>
        <li><strong>Ask Open Questions:</strong> "What's changed in your business since we last spoke?"</li>
        <li><strong>Offer Help:</strong> "I'd love to understand how we can better support your goals"</li>
        <li><strong>Set Next Steps:</strong> Always end with a clear next action or follow-up date</li>
    </ol>
</div>

{{else}}
<div class="success-notice">
    <p>üéâ <strong>Excellent Work!</strong> You have no stale leads this week. Your follow-up game is strong!</p>
</div>
{{/if}}

<div class="warning-notice">
    <p>‚è∞ <strong>Time-Sensitive:</strong> Research shows that leads contacted within 7 days have a 5x higher conversion rate. Act fast to maximize your success!</p>
</div>

<div class="info-card">
    <h4>üí° Pro Tips for Lead Re-engagement</h4>
    <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>Schedule specific times in your calendar for lead follow-ups</li>
        <li>Use the lead's preferred communication method when possible</li>
        <li>Reference specific details from previous conversations</li>
        <li>Always lead with value before asking for anything</li>
        <li>Set clear expectations for next steps</li>
    </ul>
</div>

{{/base}} 